<F P=101> ECONOMIC AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Current Demographic Statistics Viewed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Current Demographic Statistics Viewed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1386A Kiev DEMOKRATYCHNA UKRAYINA in Ukrainian 28 May 94 
pp 1-2 </F>

<F P=103> 944K1386A </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev DEMOKRATYCHNA UKRAYINA </F>
