<H3> <TI>   Survey of Food Prices in Various Cities for May 1994 </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Survey of Food Prices in Various Cities for May 1994 </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1408A Lvov ZA VILNU UKRAYINU in Ukrainian 31 May 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 944K1408A </F>
