<H3> <TI>   Official on Newly Created State Holding Company </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Official on Newly Created State Holding Company </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1380A Kiev PRAVDA UKRAINY in Russian 31 May 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 944K1380A </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev PRAVDA UKRAINY </F>
