<H3> <TI>   Deputy Minister on Situation in Mining, Smelting Industry </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Deputy Minister on Situation in Mining, Smelting Industry </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1389A Kiev PRAVDA UKRAINY in Russian 2 Jun 94 p 2 </F>
