<H3> <TI>   New Deputy Speaker Profiled </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Deputy Speaker Profiled </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1423A Lvov POST-POSTUP in Ukrainian No 18, 3-9 Jun 94 p 
A2 </F>

<F P=103> 944K1423A </F>
<F P=104>  Lvov POST-POSTUP </F>
