<H3> <TI>   State Regulation of Energy Resources Supported </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    State Regulation of Energy Resources Supported </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1229A Kiev HOLOS UKRAYINY in Ukrainian 22 Apr 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> 944K1229A </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev HOLOS UKRAYINY </F>
