<H3> <TI>   Import Duties for Food Products To Increase </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Import Duties for Food Products To Increase </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1516A Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY in Russian 7 Jun 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 944K1516A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


