<H3> <TI>     Commentary on Motives for Kuchma Appearance on Russian TV </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Commentary on Motives for Kuchma Appearance on Russian TV </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944Q0415A Moscow NEZAVISIMAYA GAZETA in Russian 7 Jun 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 944Q0415A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow NEZAVISIMAYA GAZETA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
