|              |itions (VAT --|ofits Tax -- 3|rofits Tax -- |ofits Tax -- 1| 
|              | 23, Profits |5|18|8, Plus Acce-| 
|              |Tax -- 38)   |              |              |lerated Depre-| 
|              |              |              |              |ciation       | 
