<F P=101> KAZAKHSTAN </F>
<H3> <TI>   State of Oil, Gas Industry Assessed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    State of Oil, Gas Industry Assessed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1537A Almaty PANORAMA in Russian No 24, 18 Jun 94 p 13 </F>
<F P=103> 944K1537A </F>
<F P=104>  Almaty PANORAMA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


