<H3> <TI>   Regional Energy Disputes Outlined </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Regional Energy Disputes Outlined </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1550A Almaty KAZAKHSTANSKAYA PRAVDA in Russian 21 Jun 94 
p 1 </F>

<F P=103> 944K1550A </F>
