<H3> <TI>   National Petroleum Reserves Summarized </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    National Petroleum Reserves Summarized </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1550B Almaty ABV in Russian 20 Jun 94 p 4 </F>
<F P=103> 944K1550B </F>
